# Domain components

App-specific components here; compose `src/components/ui/*`. (Nested folders under `src/components/`: extend the glob in this rule if added.)

## Wowhead (WotLK Classic)

`https://nether.wowhead.com/wotlk/tooltip/item/{itemId}`

```ts
{
  name: string;
  quality: number; // 0–7
  icon: string;
  tooltip: string; // HTML, Wowhead classes
}
```

Icon: `https://wow.zamimg.com/images/wow/icons/medium/{icon}.jpg`

| Q | Name      | Color     |
| - | --------- | --------- |
| 0 | Poor      | `#9d9d9d` |
| 1 | Common    | `#ffffff` |
| 2 | Uncommon  | `#1eff00` |
| 3 | Rare      | `#0070dd` |
| 4 | Epic      | `#a335ee` |
| 5 | Legendary | `#ff8000` |
| 6 | Artifact  | `#e6cc80` |
| 7 | Heirloom  | `#00ccff` |

## Item tooltip

`item-tooltip.tsx` — TanStack Query key `["wowhead-item", itemId]`, ~30m stale. HTML in `.wh-tooltip` + `dangerouslySetInnerHTML`; styles in `globals.css` (`.q0`–`.q8`, sockets, etc.). Border from `quality`.

## Upload log dialog

`upload-log-dialog.tsx` — trigger in sidebar; `onDoneAction` closes when flow completes. `DialogRoot`, `DialogTrigger`, `DialogContent`, …

## Upload log form

`upload-log-form.tsx` — state machine: `select` | `uploading` | `error` | `done`. XHR to `POST /api/upload`, `Content-Type: application/octet-stream`. Response type includes `raidId`, `raidName`, `raidDate`, `totalMembers`, `newMembers`. Cancel aborts XHR. Not React Hook Form (binary upload).
